次Live将会带来怎样的表演，令人期待！</p><p>那天，我准时准时加入了VRChat会场，发现自己和上次一样在海边的会场。这似乎是关椿市五番街港口设施内搭建的特殊舞台。</p><p> <a href="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/06/978416795d5a9561f4b62856d3f59be4-kix.srij09ziplo-jpg.webp" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" src="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/06/978416795d5a9561f4b62856d3f59be4-kix.srij09ziplo-1024x576.webp" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" srcset="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/06/978416795d5a9561f4b62856d3f59be4-kix.srij09ziplo-1024x576.webp 1024w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/06/978416795d5a9561f4b62856d3f59be4-kix.srij09ziplo-300x169.webp 300w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/06/978416795d5a9561f4b62856d3f59be4-kix.srij09ziplo-768x432.webp 768w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/06/978416795d5a9561f4b62856d3f59be4-kix.srij09ziplo-1536x864.webp 1536w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/06/978416795d5a9561f4b62856d3f59be4-kix.srij09ziplo-jpg.webp 1600w" width="1024" height="576" /></a></p><p>我立即换上自己的特殊虚拟角色，前往会场前方。一如既往，建筑模型的细节很好......！<strong>这种粗犷的工厂外观令人无法抗拒！ ！</strong></p><p>一名工作人员已经在那里，我们了解到，<strong>如果你触摸肥皂泡，它们就会发出声音并破裂</strong>。惊人的！已经很有趣了！ ！</p><p> <a href="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/06/978416795d5a9561f4b62856d3f59be4-kix.53z3c38hhjin-jpg.webp" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" src="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/06/978416795d5a9561f4b62856d3f59be4-kix.53z3c38hhjin-1024x576.webp" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" srcset="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/06/978416795d5a9561f4b62856d3f59be4-kix.53z3c38hhjin-1024x576.webp 1024w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/06/978416795d5a9561f4b62856d3f59be4-kix.53z3c38hhjin-300x169.webp 300w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/06/978416795d5a9561f4b62856d3f59be4-kix.53z3c38hhjin-768x432.webp 768w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/06/978416795d5a9561f4b62856d3f59be4-kix.53z3c38hhjin-1536x864.webp 1536w, 