561f4b62856d3f59be4-kix.hyaqvmom26ii-768x432.webp 768w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/06/978416795d5a9561f4b62856d3f59be4-kix.hyaqvmom26ii-1536x864.webp 1536w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/06/978416795d5a9561f4b62856d3f59be4-kix.hyaqvmom26ii-jpg.webp 1600w" width="1024" height="576" /></a></p><p><strong>黑暗中花朵色彩斑斓、温柔的光芒与音乐配合</strong>得恰到好处，有一种倦怠的魅力。 CIEL酱本身从内部发出微弱的光，光的颜色会随着声音而变化。空间制作很创新，使用包括歌手在内的整个建筑作为照明。</p><p><strong>只有右手发出柔和光芒的制作</strong>也很新鲜，营造出真正美丽而梦幻的时刻。一开始，一脸迷茫的众人一边听着，一边热情不已……</p><p> <a href="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/06/978416795d5a9561f4b62856d3f59be4-kix.2z7vfykzbj4r-jpg.webp" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" src="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/06/978416795d5a9561f4b62856d3f59be4-kix.2z7vfykzbj4r-1024x576.webp" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" srcset="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/06/978416795d5a9561f4b62856d3f59be4-kix.2z7vfykzbj4r-1024x576.webp 1024w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/06/978416795d5a9561f4b62856d3f59be4-kix.2z7vfykzbj4r-300x169.webp 300w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/06/978416795d5a9561f4b62856d3f59be4-kix.2z7vfykzbj4r-768x432.webp 768w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/06/978416795d5a9561f4b62856d3f59be4-kix.2z7vfykzbj4r-1536x864.webp 1536w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/06/978416795d5a9561f4b62856d3f59be4-kix.2z7vfykzbj4r-jpg.webp 1600w" width="1024" height="576" /></a></p><p> <a href="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/06/978416795d5a9561f4b62856d3f59be4-kix.7eb48hfet3g1-jpg.webp" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" src="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/06/978416795d5a9561f4b62856d3f59be4-kix.7eb48hfet3g1-1024x576.webp" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" srcset="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/06/978416795d5a9561f4b62856d3f59be4-kix.7eb48hfet3g1-1024x576.webp 1024w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/06/978416795d5a9561f4b62856d3f5