d5a9561f4b62856d3f59be4-kix.j1copnd2fr7i-1-768x1365.webp 768w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/06/978416795d5a9561f4b62856d3f59be4-kix.j1copnd2fr7i-1-864x1536.webp 864w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/06/978416795d5a9561f4b62856d3f59be4-kix.j1copnd2fr7i-1-jpg.webp 900w" width="576" height="1024" /></a></p><p>我想，第四首歌， <strong>“对不起，在眼睛后面。”</strong></p><p> “别照亮，好奇心”</p><p><strong><span style="font-size: 1.64em;">巴里！ ！ ！</span></strong></p><p> <a href="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/06/978416795d5a9561f4b62856d3f59be4-kix.uy6xp2a7ar8t-jpg.webp" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" src="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/06/978416795d5a9561f4b62856d3f59be4-kix.uy6xp2a7ar8t-1024x576.webp" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" srcset="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/06/978416795d5a9561f4b62856d3f59be4-kix.uy6xp2a7ar8t-1024x576.webp 1024w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/06/978416795d5a9561f4b62856d3f59be4-kix.uy6xp2a7ar8t-300x169.webp 300w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/06/978416795d5a9561f4b62856d3f59be4-kix.uy6xp2a7ar8t-768x432.webp 768w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/06/978416795d5a9561f4b62856d3f59be4-kix.uy6xp2a7ar8t-1536x864.webp 1536w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/06/978416795d5a9561f4b62856d3f59be4-kix.uy6xp2a7ar8t-jpg.webp 1600w" width="1024" height="576" /></a></p><p>夏尔唱歌并摇动手臂的那一刻，</p><p><strong><span style="font-size: 1.64em;">空间裂开，仿佛雷霆落下！ ！ ！ ！</span></strong></p><p><strong><span style="font-size: 1.64em;">惊喜！ ！ ！ ！</span></strong></p><p>当然，这首歌阴暗而激烈，气氛一下子就变了。突然<strong>，头顶下起了倾盆大雨，玻璃碎片飘浮在空间中，随着声音剧烈切换的灯光反射得那么耀眼</strong>。透过雨滴和玻璃的倒影，夏尔露出严肃的表情。玻璃闪闪发光，仿佛随着歌曲的快节奏而跳动，像失重的力量一样在太空中翱翔。<br /> <a href="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/06/978416795d5a9561f4b62856d3f59be4-kix.8pecdodln4a5-jpg.webp" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" src="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/06/978416795d5a9561f4b62856d3f59be4-kix.8pecdodln4a5-1024x576.webp" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" srcset="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/06/978416795d5a9561f4b62856d3f59be4-kix.8pecdodln4a5-1024x576.webp 1024w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/06/978416795d5a9561f4b62856d3f59be4-kix.8pecdodln4a5-300x169.webp 300w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/06/978416795d5a9561f4b62856d3f59be4-kix.8pecdodln4a5-768x432.webp 768w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/06/978416795d5a9561f4b62856d3f59be4-kix.8pecdodln4a5-1536x864.webp 1536w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/06/978416795d5a9561f4b62856d3f59be4-kix.8pecdodln4a5-jpg.webp 1600w" width="1024" height="576" /></a><br /> <a href="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/06/978416795d5a9561f4b62856d3f59be4-kix.6pv57saw8yya-jpg.webp" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" src="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/06/978416795d5a9561f4b62856d3f59be4-kix.6pv57saw8yya-1024x576.webp" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" srcset="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/06/978416795d5a9561f4b62856d3f59be4-kix.6pv57saw8yya-1024x576.webp 1024w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/06/978416795d5a9561f4b62856d3f59be4-kix.6pv57saw8yya-300x169.webp 300w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/06/978416795d5a9561f4b62856d3f59be4-kix.6pv57saw8yya-768x432.webp 768w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/06/978416795d5a9561f4b62856d3f59be4-kix.6pv57saw8yya-1536x864.webp 1536w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/06/978416795d5a9561f4b62856d3f59be4-kix.6pv57saw8yya-jpg.webp 1600w" width="1024" height="576" /></a> <a href="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/06/978416795d5a9561f4b62856d3f59be4-kix.nlxxayxk3kwz-jpg.webp" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" src="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/06/978416795d5a9561f4b62856d3f59be4-kix.nlxxayxk3kwz-576x1024.webp" sizes="(max-width: 576px) 100vw, 576px" srcset="https://assets.moguravr.com/u